com.hp.ov.sdk.rest.client

Interface FcSansProviderClient

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FcSansProviderClientImpl

    public interface FcSansProviderClient
    A provider is a software plugin for the SAN Resource Manager that enables the resource manager to communicate with some kind of device that provides SAN network zoning. For example, The SAN Resource Manager includes a provider that communicates with Brocade Network Advisor or HP SAN Network Advisor systems, and another that communicates with HP 5900 series switches.
